                  "Value": "ISO symbol, For diabetes, sensory disorders of the skin, circulatory and lymphatic drainage disorders and skin diseases consult a doctor before use. Do not use the support in combination with other compression products, creams, skin oils, etc.  Creams and oils can affect the gel pad. In the event of tingling or numbness during the use, or white or violet colouring of the skin, remove the bandage immediately or loosen. Do not wear while sleeping or during prolonged resting periods. Wearing for a maximum of 16 hours per day. Discontinue use if skin irritation occurs and consult a doctor if this persists. Discontinue use if if the elasticity of the bandage decreases, the gel pad has been damaged, or the Velcro no longer closes properly. Store in the original packaging. This contains important information. Inform the manufacturer and the competent authority about serious incidents. "
